title: What are the top ten best Led Zeppelin tracks? - Quora

response.answer_text: This is the list which most of the classic rock lovers like me would like Here is my top ten Led Zeppelin tracks : Whole Lotta Love (i like the medley version)Stairway to Heaven (i like the live version)Immigrant SongRock and Roll (i like the live version)HeartbreakerGood Times Bad TimesCommunication BreakdownBlack DogDazed and ConfusedKashmirRamble Onif you like all this songs you might as well like songs from this new classic rock album also check this on YouTube, Apple , GooglePlay , etc ..
